BT /F1 10 Tf 82 588 Td (authentication service on 2026-02-26, 14:12-14:59 ET. Approximately 6.2% of login attempts) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 574 Td (failed during the window.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 72 552 Td (2. Root Cause) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 530 Td (A configuration change to the OAuth token-signing service deployed a rotated signing key) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 516 Td (without propagating the public key to all validation nodes. Validation nodes in the us-) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 502 Td (east region rejected tokens signed with the new key, producing HTTP 401 responses for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 488 Td (affected sessions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 462 Td (The change passed staging because the staging cluster shares a single key-distribution) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 448 Td (node, masking the propagation gap that exists in the multi-region production topology.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 72 426 Td (3. Resolution & Action Items) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 404 Td (Mitigation: rolled back the key rotation at 14:51 ET; full recovery by 14:59 ET. Action) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 390 Td (items: \(1\) add a cross-region key-propagation health check to the deploy pipeline -- owner) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 376 Td (Sameer Patel, due 2026-03-13; \(2\) require a canary in a multi-node validation cluster) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 362 Td (before production rollout -- owner Rachel Okonkwo, due 2026-03-20; \(3\) add alerting on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 82 348 Td (401-rate deltas per region -- owner Tony Briggs, due 2026-03-06.) Tj ET
